</div><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-primary shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">groups</span></div></div><div><h4 class=\"font-headline font-semibold text-lg text-on-surface\">Collaborate</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant mt-1 leading-relaxed\">We&#x27;ll discuss sketches and yarn swatches via WhatsApp to perfect the vision.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-5\"><div class=\"flex-shrink-0\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-primary shadow-sm\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">auto_awesome</span></div></div><div><h4 class=\"font-headline font-semibold text-lg text-on-surface\">Create</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant mt-1 leading-relaxed\">Sit back as I translate our conversation into a tactile manuscript of yarn.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-primary/5 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-primary/10 flex flex-col items-center text-center\"><div class=\"w-24 h-24 rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-4 border-2 border-primary relative\"><img class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\" alt=\"Portrait of Reena\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCPQ1LCPW2Zyc6mmNLNuotPr7y4oWcWsJzrjkRS1f9RQ3HMwqOCeFyMfE_GJMsE1Hjs7AwMt1fy-FlgvcyzMKGnBmDdjUMJvYmTkNcK_p4Hs4AJ53reBXUKU_CB_DPnG2-ExaNUv4OVT_TkBRCXIq3UMAQ-Y7nABC8lrnd8ultcjf48NXNb1oqvK5A1Td4Z1U6t6I9Q07kLU_1LH3So4ns66sP1AYpV34DOZDbwBZJZmDNdJY5n54dCxFZJ1VpLqG5s8c_aCZ-c-2s\"/></div><h4 class=\"font-serif italic text-xl text-primary mb-2\">Reena&#x27;s Atelier</h4><span class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-tertiary-fixed text-on-tertiary-fixed rounded-full text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-tighter mb-4\">Master Artisan</span><p class=\"text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed italic\">&quot;Every stitch carries a heartbeat. I can&#x27;t wait to see what story we&#x27;ll tell next.&quot;</p></div></as